<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<title>Example of CSS3 animation Property</title>
<style type="text/css">
.box {
    width: 103px;
    height: 130px;
	margin: 50px;
    background: url("/examples/images/octopus.png") no-repeat;
    position: relative;
    /* Chrome, Safari, Opera */
    -webkit-animation: moveit 2s linear 0s infinite alternate;
    /* Standard syntax */
    animation: moveit 2s linear 0s infinite alternate;
}
 
/* Chrome, Safari, Opera */
@-webkit-keyframes moveit {
    from {left: 0;}
    to {left: 50%;}
}
 
/* Standard syntax */
@keyframes moveit {
    from {left: 0;}
    to {left: 50%;}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="box"></div>
</body>
</html>    
